author: Source: Harwich and Manningtree Standard
title: Wayne Rooney to miss England's final two Euro 2016 qualifiers - Harwich and Manningtree Standard
text:
Wayne Rooney will miss England's final Euro 2016 qualifier away to Lithuania on Monday as well as Friday's clash with Estonia at Wembley, manager Roy Hodgson has confirmed. The captain has a minor ankle injury and Hodgson said he would be "devastated" should the Manchester United striker exacerbate the problem while on international duty.
 Harwich and Manningtree Standard.
